subject: Lacrosse
College Athletics
NCAA Lacrosse Championships
lead_paragraph: Rob Pannell, who delayed his graduation so that he could play another season after breaking a bone in his foot last year, will lead his team against Duke in the N.C.A.A. semifinals Saturday.
